# ============================================================
# Manual Annotations — Turkish Morphological Disambiguation
# Annotator: Akif Adnan
# Format: CoNLL-U (Universal Dependencies)
# Columns: ID FORM LEMMA UPOS XPOS FEATS HEAD DEPREL DEPS MISC
# Notes:
#   - UPOS tags follow Universal Dependencies v2 guidelines
#   - FEATS include Case, Number, Person, Tense, Mood, Polarity
#   - HEAD/DEPREL left as _ (outside scope of this project)
#   - B = begin span, I = inside span (BIO where applicable)
# ============================================================

